### 1. Login to get Access Token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password"
}

### Variable to store token
@authToken = {{login.response.body.access_token}}

### 2. Create a Doctor (Requires Admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/doctors
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userid": "2", 
    "name": "Dr. Gregory House",
    "specialization": "Diagnostician",
    "phone": "555-0199",
    "email": "house@clinic.com"
}

### 3. Get All Doctors
GET http://localhost:3000/doctors
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 4. Create a Patient
POST http://localhost:3000/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "dateofbirth": "1985-07-20",
  "gender": "Male",
  "phone": "555-1234",
  "address": "123 Baker St"
}

### 5. Get All Patients
GET http://localhost:3000/patients
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 6. Create Appointment
POST http://localhost:3000/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientid": 1,
  "doctorid": 1,
  "appointmenttime": "2025-12-25T10:00:00.000Z",
  "notes": "Regular checkup"
}

### 7. Get Appointments
GET http://localhost:3000/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 8. Create Medicine (Pharmacy)
POST http://localhost:3000/medicines
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Paracetamol",
  "quantity": 100,
  "price": 5.50
}

### 9. Get Medicines
GET http://localhost:3000/medicines
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
